394
00:21:10.978 --> 00:21:12.688  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I really hope that's metaphorical.

395
00:21:13.438 --> 00:21:17.317  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
You're so lucky, you don't even know.
You have all this freedom.

396
00:21:17.401 --> 00:21:20.195  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
That freedom's been
a real boon to me lately.

397
00:21:20.279 --> 00:21:22.531  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
But at least you get to do what you want.

398
00:21:22.614 --> 00:21:24.700  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
